commentText:
Set the specific redirect 3xx status code to use.__

If not set, {@link org.springframework.web.servlet.view.RedirectView}_will select {@code HttpStatus.MOVED_TEMPORARILY (302)} by default.
codeText: public RedirectViewControllerRegistration setStatusCode(HttpStatus statusCode) {_		Assert.isTrue(statusCode.is3xxRedirection(), "Not a redirect status code.")__		this.redirectView.setStatusCode(statusCode)__		return this__	}

commentText:
Whether to propagate the query parameters of the current request through_to the target redirect URL.__

Default is {@code false}.
codeText: public RedirectViewControllerRegistration setKeepQueryParams(boolean propagate) {_		this.redirectView.setPropagateQueryParams(propagate)__		return this__	}
